      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i need help figuring something out. i've noticed something really weird with my smart thermostat and my smart fridge. every time i get really stressed or start crying, the thermostat temp drops like 3 degrees almost instantly. and the fridge? the light stays on way longer than usual when i'm upset. it's like they know. is there any way they could be linked or sensing something?",
